description: This file declares the exported API functions for a component dealing with unsigned integer arrays within the RDK BroadWay Service Delivery System. It contains function prototypes for creating, removing, enrolling, and initializing the component.

methods.name: AnscCreateUIntArrayComponent
methods.description: Creates a new UInt Array component instance with specified container, owner, and reserved contexts.

methods.name: AnscUIntArrayCOCreate
methods.description: Initializes a new UInt Array component with specified contexts.

methods.name: AnscUIntArrayCORemove
methods.description: Removes and cleans up the specified UInt Array component instance.

methods.name: AnscUIntArrayCOEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls the necessary objects or dependencies for the UInt Array component.

methods.name: AnscUIntArrayCOInitialize
methods.description: Performs initialization routines for the UInt Array component.
